{% block subject %}{{ title }} talk confirmation{% endblock %}

{% block from %}{{ email }}{% endblock %}
{% block from_name %}{{ title }}{% endblock %}

{% block body_html %}
    <p>
        Thanks for submitting your talk for {{ title }} {{ arrival || date_format('Y') }} Digital Edition!
    </p>
    <p>
        Submitted Talk Title: "{{ talk }}"
    </p>
    <p>
        The deadline to apply to our CFP is {{ enddate }}. We will let you know about your proposal 3 weeks after the
        closing date.
        In the meantime, please share that you submitted your talk for {{ title }} {{ arraival || date_format('Y') }} on
        your social and ask your followers to vote for your topic on this form: http://tiny.cc/{{ title }}topics
    </p>
    <p>
        We will also evaluate the proposals based on the topics selected by the community ;)
    </p>
    <p>
        No idea what to write? Here is some ready-made copy you can use
        <a href="https://sites.google.com/grusp.org/partner/{{ title }}/copy"></a>
    </p>
    <p>
        Do you want to tweet about it? Click <a href="http://tiny.cc/CFPfilledin-{{ title }}">here</a>
    </p>
    <p> As a small token of appreciation for submitting a talk, here is a 5% discount to share with your contacts:
        CFP_{{ title }}_OFF5
    </p>
    <p> Should you need assistance, please do not hesitate to contact us.
    </p>
    <p>
        Thanks again and good Luck!<br>
        The {{ title }} Team
    </p>
{% endblock %}

